stateDiagram-v2
    %% Manual Summary (US1) - State Diagram

    [*] --> IDLE : modal opened

    IDLE --> LOADING : user selects time range / generate()
    LOADING --> HAS_SUMMARY : API returns summaryData with messages > 0
    LOADING --> NO_MESSAGES : API returns summaryData with messages === 0
    LOADING --> ERROR : API error or network failure

    ERROR --> LOADING : user retries

    HAS_SUMMARY --> LOADING : user changes time range preset
    NO_MESSAGES --> LOADING : user changes time range preset

    IDLE --> [*] : onClose
    LOADING --> [*] : onClose
    HAS_SUMMARY --> [*] : onClose
    NO_MESSAGES --> [*] : onClose
    ERROR --> [*] : onClose

    note right of IDLE
        Modal rendered via portal
        Time presets shown: 30m, 1h, 3h
    end note

    note right of LOADING
        POST /api/summaries/manual
        isLoading = true, spinner shown
    end note

    note right of HAS_SUMMARY
        Displays: overview, keyTopics,
        mostActiveUsers, importantMessages, stats
    end note

    note right of ERROR
        Displays error message
        Retry button available
    end note
